metadata.name: "Love is...ERROR"
metadata.description:
do you remember her eyes when you first met her?
do you remember her smell when you hugged her?
do you remember her touch when she took your hand?
do you remember the time when the earth went out from under your feet just from the thought of being together?

this little devil blows your head off...
and maybe this is the stupidest thing you've done...
all analysis and self-control have lost at least some meaning... 
you feel...means alive...

Love is...ERROR...ERROR...ERrr0r////err98ror...erro003/'/';'/"2@#$$@@#$@ t
